'''约翰·彼得·里克茨'''（John Peter Ricketts；{{bd|1964年|8月19日}}）是[[美國|美國]][[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]的一位政治人物<ref>{{cite news|last1=Hammel|first1=Paul|title=Platte Institute: Overhauled Nebraska tax system could drive more jobs|url=http://www.omaha.com/news/platte-institute-overhauled-nebraska-tax-system-could-drive-more-jobs/article_8c9a2108-5d83-52ee-a8d0-c8767cc6b9c5.html|accessdate=2015-07-02|publisher=''Omaha World-Herald''|date=2013-10-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Duggan|first1=Joe|title=After failed tuneup in 2006, Pete Ricketts says he's road-tested and ready to lead|url=http://www.omaha.com/news/politics/after-failed-tuneup-in-pete-ricketts-says-he-s-road/article_c8652891-e11c-5d43-ab7a-e5bb1b82ecbe.html|accessdate=2015-07-02|publisher=''Omaha World-Herald''|date=2014-10-19|archive-date=2018-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181010120359/https://www.omaha.com/news/politics/after-failed-tuneup-in-pete-ricketts-says-he-s-road/article_c8652891-e11c-5d43-ab7a-e5bb1b82ecbe.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。皮特·里克茨自2015年開始擔任第40任[[內布拉斯加州|內布拉斯加州]]州長。他在踏入政壇之前曾經是一名商人。在{{le|2006年美国内布拉斯加州参议院选举|2006 United States Senate election in Nebraska|2006年}}，里克茨曾經競選內布拉斯加州州参议员，但未當選。{{le|2014年内布拉斯加州州长选举|2014 Nebraska gubernatorial election|2014年}}競選内布拉斯加州州长並當選，{{le|2018年内布拉斯加州州长选举|2018 Nebraska gubernatorial election|2018年}}再次竞选并成功连任。

==政治立场==
===死刑===
里基茨是[[死刑|死刑]]的狂热支持者<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/08/03/us/nebraska-death-penalty-execution.html|title=Pope's Death Penalty Stance Won't Stop Execution, Nebraska's Catholic Governor Says|publisher=|accessdate=2018-08-03|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109042945/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/08/03/us/nebraska-death-penalty-execution.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。他通过表明他的宗教信仰支持死刑的来证明他的立场是正确的。然而，长期存在的天主教出版物和教会领袖（包括教皇[[若望保禄二世|若望保禄二世]]和教皇[[方济各_(教宗)|方济各]]）的官方声明都彻底谴责了死刑<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ncronline.org/news/people/nebraska-catholic-bishops-oppose-execution-death-row-inmate |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-05-11 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128024330/https://www.ncronline.org/news/people/nebraska-catholic-bishops-oppose-execution-death-row-inmate |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
===大麻===
里基茨反对[[药用大麻|药用大麻]]合法化。2019年，他表示，大麻的“药用价值尚未测试”，并引用研究表明，大麻对大脑功能有不利影响。他还指出，过量服用{{le|合成大麻素K2|Synthetic cannabinoids}}提醒人们，大麻有多危险。<ref>{{cite web | last1=Ricketts | first1=Pete | title=Marijuana Is a Dangerous Drug | url=https://governor.nebraska.gov/press/marijuana-dangerous-drug | date= | publisher=Office of Gov. Pete Ricketts | accessdate=2019-08-16 | archive-date=2021-03-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317023309/https://governor.nebraska.gov/press/marijuana-dangerous-drug | dead-url=no }}</ref> 
===环境===
里基茨表示，他支持{{le|拱心石管道|Keystone Pipeline}}建设，他表示，该管道将在内布拉斯加州创造就业机会，在内布拉斯加州创造大量税收，显然有助于我们减少对外国石油的依赖。<ref>{{cite web | last1=Brown | first1=Ben | title=Gov. Ricketts on Keystone: Being Less Dependent on Foreign Oil is a Big Deal | url=http://www.foxbusiness.com/politics/2017/05/05/gov-ricketts-on-keystone-being-less-dependent-on-foreign-oil-is-big-deal.html | date=2017-05-05 | publisher=[[福斯财经网|福斯财经网]] | accessdate=2017-05-05 | archive-date=2017-08-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170820160840/http://www.foxbusiness.com/politics/2017/05/05/gov-ricketts-on-keystone-being-less-dependent-on-foreign-oil-is-big-deal.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

